snippet.title: The Cosmic Wheel Sisterhood | Tarot Card Design Overview
snippet.description:
In this new trailer you can see The Cosmic Wheel Sisterhood’s card creation and customisation in action and learn how to use the power you’ve awakened to gaze into the future.

The elements you combine on your cards will determine their meaning, letting you read the fortunes of a diverse group of witches to determine the trajectory of their lives and the fate of your coven.

The Cosmic Wheel Sisterhood is coming to PC and Switch later this year. Visit http://cosmicwheelsisterhood.com for more information.
